    • Project

      public Project​(String number, String name, String buildingType, String address, int erfNumber, float totalFee, float totalPaid, String deadlineDate, Person architect, Person contractor, Person customer, String projectCompleted)
      Project constructor method.
      The method used to generate new project objects.
      Parameters:
      number - project number
      name - project name
      buildingType - the building type of the project e.g. house, apartment
      address - building address
      erfNumber - property ERF number
      totalFee - total cost of the project
      totalPaid - amount paid up until this point
      deadlineDate - expected date of completion
      architect - Person object containing details of project architect
      contractor - Person object containing details of project contractor
      customer - Person object containing details of project customer
      projectCompleted - boolean indicating whether project is completed
      Since:
      version 1.00
